name: MetaLand
description: it may seem like a dystopian future but MetaLand is much more current than you can imagine, in the speculative system associated with NFT there are occasions when a whale brings out an unknown artist just to be able to earn from his works bought first at a low price, and then when the hype for the artist decreases the whale disappears leaving him alone in the middle of the sea to drown in silence. All of this is increasingly encouraged by the high competitiveness of marketplaces where the density of artists is so high that it is very easy to fall under the temptation to rely on a curatorship, destroying the fundamental principles of cryptoart.
